  08 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> patchage-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Drop old Python implementations

  23 Mar 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> -files/ldconfig.patch,
  -patchage-0.4.4.ebuild, -patchage-0.4.5.ebuild, -patchage-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Remove old superseded versions.

  03 Jan 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> patchage-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Add PYTHON_REQ_USE as necessary for waf.

  12 Oct 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> -patchage-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Cleanup old EAPI1

  12 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> patchage-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #518782

  28 Sep 2014; Chema Alonso <nimiux@gentoo.org> patchage-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64 wrt bug #518782

  30 Jan 2014; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> patchage-0.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Move boost to DEPEND since it appears only headers are required.

*patchage-0.5.0-r1 (30 Jan 2014)

